plot: The affair between Naomi and Emily intensifies. Cook is running for student president and challenges Naomi to sleep with him if he wins. He does win, but they get no further than kissing. Meanwhile, Freddie tells Naomi that he has fallen out with Cook and loves Effy. Naomi resists the advances of her teacher Kieran to have sex with Emily again, then finds Kieran in bed with her mother. She ends up holding hands with Emily through a catflap.—don @ minifie-1
